This paper deals with the problem of keyword search on RDF data, which is a typical task in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The paper proposes a novel approach for assembling a query graph based on the input keywords, which involves techniques from information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), deep learning (cs.DL), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these sub-categories are likely to be relevant to this paper.
